error.signature: Error [ERR_PACKAGE_PATH_NOT_EXPORTED]: Package subpath './internal' is not defined by exports

verdict.summary: Importing a subpath that the package's exports map doesn't expose.

dead_ends.action: Patching node_modules to add the export
dead_ends.why_fails: Will be overwritten on next npm install
Bypasses package boundaries; may break with updates
